 the wing of\nthe SiIV lines, although in one case a very weak absorption feature was\ndetected. No motions, indicative of jets, were detected in SJ or AIA images.\nReconnection in an asymmetric magnetic-field geometry, in the middle or near\nthe top of small loops is a plausible explanation of their observational\ncharacteristics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2023 21:09:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-08"}
