\ntemperature, and the DT of a real-world drone with the capability of\nforecasting its trajectory in an outdoor scenario.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2023 09:37:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-19"}
