eneralised to apply\nfor all high charge state ECR ion sources. Finally, we present the results of\nsystematic plasma potential measurements of the Phoenix-type CB-ECRIS at LPSC,\nvarying the source potential, the microwave power and the axial magnetic field\nsrength. It was observed that the plasma potential increases with the\nextraction magnetic field and the microwave power.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2023 09:48:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Mar 2023 07:32:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-26"}
