 twisting angle dependence of NFRHT, different from the\noscillation phenomenon of NFRHT for particle gratings mediated by the\nintra-ensemble and inter-ensemble MBI. This work will deepen the understanding\nof the NFRHT in dense particulate systems and guide applications for thermal\nmanagement in micro-/nano-electromechanical devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2023 13:14:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-19"}
